        <h1 id="top">MISQ Policies for Publication</h1>
        <p>To maintain the highest standards of research quality, all parties involved in the publication of the <em>Management Information Systems Quarterly</em> (<em>MIS Quarterly</em>) must comply with the following policies and guidelines, which include, but are not limited to:</p>
        <div class="layout">
        <nav class="toc" aria-label="Table of contents">
        <strong>Contents</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#s1">1. Journal Overview</a></li>
